# 5: Mouse and Key bindings
#
# Contexts:
#     R = Root Window                 rrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr
#     W = Application Window          rIrrrr<---------^rrrrr
#     F = Frame Corners               rrrrrr[13TTTT642]rrrrr
#     S = Frame Sides                 rIrrrr[wwwwwwwww]rrrrr
#     T = Title Bar                   rrrrrr[wwwwwwwww]rrrrr
#     I = Icon                        rIrrrrv_________>rrrrr
#     A = Any                         rrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr
#
#     Numbers are buttons: [1 3 5 7 9  TTTTT  0 8 6 4 2]
#
# Modifiers: (A)ny, (C)ontrol, (S)hift, (M)eta, (N)othing
#
# Format: Key <X>  <Context> <Modifier> <Action>
#         Mouse <X> <Context> <Modifier> <Action>
####################

# Alt-F1 or Menu to load the root menu and Alt-Tab for a WindowList.
# Super-1/2/3/4+... will switch between the Virtual Desktops.
# Super_R (windows key) will launch a terminal.
# "4" is the modifier for Super/Windows key. "M" (Meta) is alt.

# Silent supresses any errors (such as keyboards with no Menu key).

# General Bindings
# Root Menu
Silent Key F1 A M Menu MenuFvwmRoot
Silent Key Menu A A Menu MenuFvwmRoot

# Rofi
Silent Key a A 4 Exec exec rofi -dpi `xrdb -q | grep Xft.dpi | sed --expression='s/Xft.dpi://'` -show drun -show-icons -display-drun "Applications"
Silent Key w A 4 Exec exec rofi -dpi `xrdb -q | grep Xft.dpi | sed --expression='s/Xft.dpi://'` -show window -show-icons -kb-accept-entry '!Alt-Tab,!Alt-ISO_Left_Tab,Return' -kb-row-down 'Alt-Tab,Alt-Down,Down' -kb-row-up 'Alt-ISO_Left_Tab,Alt-Up,Up' -kb-cancel "Alt-Escape,Escape" -display-window "All Windows"
Silent Key e A 4 Exec exec rofi -dpi `xrdb -q | grep Xft.dpi | sed --expression='s/Xft.dpi://'` -show filebrowser 
Silent Key q A 4 Exec exec rofi -show power-menu -modi power-menu:'~/.config/rofi/rofi-power-menu' -no-show-icons
Silent Key Tab A M WindowList Root c c CurrentAtEnd, CurrentDesk, NoDeskNum, SelectOnRelease Alt_L
Silent Key Tab A MS WindowList Root c c CurrentAtEnd, CurrentDesk, NoDeskNum, SelectOnRelease Alt_L
Silent Key Return A 4 Exec exec $[infostore.terminal]
Silent Key XF86Search	A A	Exec exec rofi -dpi `xrdb -q | grep Xft.dpi | sed --expression='s/Xft.dpi://'` -show drun -show-icons -display-drun "Applications"

# FVWM stuff
Silent Key i A 4 Module FvwmIdent
Silent Key r A 4 Refresh
Silent Key r A 4S Restart
Silent Key q A 4S Quit

# Lock screen: Device-dependent
Silent Key l A 4 Exec exec sh $HOME/.config/systemlockscript

# Raise/Lower (up/down)
Silent Key u A 4 Raise
Silent Key d A 4 Lower

# Window Actions
Silent Key f A 4 Maximize 100 100
Silent Key c A 4S Close
Silent Key Space A M Menu MenuWindowOps Delete
Silent Key F10 A S Menu MenuWindowOps Delete
Silent Key D A 4S Destroy
Silent Key m A 4 Iconify
Silent Key s A 4 WindowShade
Silent Key p A 4 Stick
Silent Key t A 4 Pick (CirculateHit) ToggleTitle
# Focus next and previous windows
Silent Key z A 4 Prev Focus
Silent Key x A 4 Next Focus

# Tiling (basic)
Silent Key Left A 4 TileLeft
Silent Key Right A 4 TileRight
Silent Key Up A 4 TileTop
Silent Key Down A 4 TileBottom

# Corner Tiling (; ' . /)
Silent Key semicolon A 4 TileTopLeft
Silent Key apostrophe A 4 TileTopRight
Silent Key period A 4 TileBottomLeft
Silent Key slash A 4 TileBottomRight

# Moving Windows (position)
Silent Key Left A 4M Move w-1 keep
Silent Key Right A 4M Move w+1 keep
Silent Key Up A 4M Move keep w-1
Silent Key Down A 4M Move keep w+1

# Moving Windows (snap until next window)
Silent Key Left A 4C Move shuffle Left
Silent Key Right A 4C Move shuffle Right
Silent Key Up A 4C Move shuffle Up
Silent Key Down A 4C Move shuffle Down

# Resizing Windows
Silent Key Left A 4S Resize w-1 keep
Silent Key Right A 4S Resize w+1 keep
Silent Key Up A 4S Resize keep w-1
Silent Key Down A 4S Resize keep w+1

# Virtual desktops
# Go to
Silent Key Tab A 4 GoToDesk 1 0 10
Silent Key Tab A 4S GoToDesk -1 0 10
Silent Key 1 A 4 GotoDesk 0 0
Silent Key 2 A 4 GotoDesk 0 1
Silent Key 3 A 4 GotoDesk 0 2
Silent Key 4 A 4 GotoDesk 0 3
Silent Key 5 A 4 GotoDesk 0 4
Silent Key 6 A 4 GotoDesk 0 5
Silent Key 7 A 4 GotoDesk 0 6
Silent Key 8 A 4 GotoDesk 0 7
Silent Key 9 A 4 GotoDesk 0 8
Silent Key 0 A 4 GotoDesk 0 9
# Move to other desktop
Silent Key 1 A 4S MoveToDesk 0 0
Silent Key 2 A 4S MoveToDesk 0 1
Silent Key 3 A 4S MoveToDesk 0 2
Silent Key 4 A 4S MoveToDesk 0 3
Silent Key 5 A 4S MoveToDesk 0 4
Silent Key 6 A 4S MoveToDesk 0 5
Silent Key 7 A 4S MoveToDesk 0 6
Silent Key 8 A 4S MoveToDesk 0 7
Silent Key 9 A 4S MoveToDesk 0 8
Silent Key 0 A 4S MoveToDesk 0 9

